  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "AI가 응답 후 트래커 JSON 추가. ScenePulse가 자동 추출 및 숨김.",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "AI가 트래커 누락 시 ScenePulse가 별도 API로 복구. 프로필 필요.",
